name: Techmox
overview: Startup job search provider, Techmox, announces its launch as an Information Technology-specific job board providing service in matching IT professionals with industry employers. Featuring a sleek and modern look, Techmox employs a simple solution for IT job seekers who wish to discover new opportunities within their field. For employers, Techmox offers considerably lower job posting fees than competing job sites, allowing the site to accumulate many listings and grow at a considerably fast pace. Information Technology professionals are highly specialized and Techmox provides a targeted service for these individuals, demonstrating the value for employers to use Techmox’s niche service.
